project_address: Dafnala road Near Ghevar Circle , Shahibaug
promoterAddress: 402, Center Plaza, Opp Sarthak School,  Ghatlodiya, Ahmedabad Ahmedabad 380054

formThreeBId.notesToCertificate:
1. On the basis of information given and records & documents provided to me, the partnership firm has borrowed monies from friends and relatives for development of project. The partnership firm does not have any outstanding loan from Banks or financial institutions for development of the above mentioned project.					
2. The audit for FY 2019-20, FY 2020-21 & FY 2021-22 as per Income Tax Act 1961 is pending while issuing this certificate. So the certificate is issued based on unaudited books of accounts.					
3. In some of the units where amount received is more than 10% of the unit value but no Agreement to sale has been made.					
4. During the period 01.12.2021 to 28.02.2022 the amount of Rs. 40,00,000/- received from member as collection have been deposited into RERA Collection account but 70% of Same amounting to Rs. 28,00,000/- have not been transferred to RERA retention account.					
5. Interest payable on unsecured loans have been debited to P&L A/c. but it has been reinvested as unsecured loans and Audit for F.Y. 2021-22 is also pending so bifurcation of interest into specific project has not been made and hence not taken into consideration in form.					
6. As per the information and explanation given and records & documents provided to me by the partners of the firm, the partnership firm has borrowed monies from various persons for development of the projects of the firm. Unsecured loans have not been borrowed for any specific project and it is a general loan for all the projects and hence it is not possible for me to bifurcate these borrowed amount to a specific project and hence the amount of loans shown here above are the total borrowings for all the projects of the partnership firm. The partnership firm does not have any outstanding loan from Banks or Financial Institutions for development of the above mentioned project.
